Sendmsg: 
1. Non-exist cert
    - ./sendmsg client.pem addleness (single recipient)
    - ./sendmsg client.pem addleness analects (multiple recipients)
2. Invalid recipient name(s)
    - ./sendmsg client.cert.pem addle (single recipient)
    - ./sendmsg client.cert.pem a#a analects (multiple recipients/partial invalid)
    - ./sendmsg client.cert.pem !// _analects (multiple recipients/all invalid) (bash: !//: event not found)
3. (Should we limit the number of recipients in a single sendmsg?)